Read the implementation spec at `.hanness/pages/page_07_win_lose.page` and implement everything described.

Prerequisites: page_03 (GameScene) and page_06 (HUD) must be complete.

Steps:
1. Create `client/src/logic/WinLoseChecker.js` with checkSolo(), checkPvP(), saveBestScore(), loadBestScore().
2. Create `client/src/scenes/ResultScene.js` with solo and PvP result layouts.
3. Wire _onDefeat() into GameScene.update() for solo mode.
4. Wire _onGameOver() handler for PvP GAME_OVER socket event.
5. Implement localStorage save on defeat with comparison to previous best.
6. Add Restart and Back-to-Lobby buttons in ResultScene.

After implementing, verify each acceptance criterion listed at the bottom of the spec.
